# Personal Portfolio Website

## Description

A simple HTML portfolio website to practice basic HTML structure and semantic tags.

## HTML Tags Used

<html> – Defines the HTML document.
<head> – Contains webpage information.
<title> – Displays the page title in the browser tab.
<body> – Contains all visible webpage content.
<header> – Represents the top section of the webpage.
<h1>– Displays the main heading.
<nav> – Creates a navigation menu.
<a> – Creates hyperlinks.
<section> – Groups related content into sections.
<h2> – Displays section headings.
<img> – Displays an image.
<p> – Defines a paragraph.
<ul> – Creates an unordered list.
<li> – Defines a list item.
<footer> – Represents the bottom section of the webpage.
